The paper deals with discrepancy minimization, which is a topic in theoretical computer science related to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also uses techniques from information theory (cs.IT) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The problem of discrepancy minimization is closely related to geometric combinatorics (cs.CG) and game theory (cs.GT), which are also mentioned in the paper.
